(11, 1, '2016-11-18 16:42:10', '2016-11-18 16:42:10', '<p>Kidizens is an innovative educational environment where students build and inhabit their own LEGO city. We encourage collaborative and guided discovery of real-world concepts while role-playing and having fun in a universe built of LEGOs.<br>\r\nOur goal is to inspire kids to become great citizens and future leaders, one LEGO brick at a time. We believe that our teaching and learning philosophies nurture critical thinking skills, preparing kids for the 21st century. Take our virtual tour to learn more about the world of Kidizens or read more about <a title="Program Overview" href="http://thekidizens.com/?page_id=338">how it works</a>.</p>\r\n<h5>Age Appropriate Program Options</h5>\r\n<p>We offer multiple age-appropriate Kidizens program options for students:</p>\r\n<div class="listing program-list">\r\n<p><b>Young Kidizens</b> – Age 6-8<br/>\r\n<b>Kidizens</b> – Age 8-11<br/>\r\n<b>Kidizens Leadership Program</b> – Age 10-13<br/>\r\n<b>Robotizens</b> – Age 8-12<br/>\r\n<b>Young Senators</b> – Age 9-12<br/>\r\n<b>Young Entrepreneurs</b> – Age 8-12</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>We also offer special workshops, birthday parties, and drop-in sessions to supplement our standard program offerings.\r\nSpace is limited and our programs fill up quickly. View our schedule to see upcoming registration times and our pricing options to learn more.</p>\r\n<h5>Building the Skills Today to Lead Our World Tomorrow</h5>\r\n<p>Research has shown that students learn more when they are provided with fun and interactive experiences that engage their senses and stimulate creative thinking. By registering your child for Kidizens, they’ll not only get play with LEGOs, they’ll learn important life skills including:</p>\r\n<div class="table-main">\r\n<div class="program-table">\r\n   <div class="left-p">\r\n      <p>\r\nSpatial and conceptual development</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class="left-p">\r\n     <p>\r\nProblem-solving and analytical skills<p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="program-table">\r\n   <div class="left-p">\r\n      <p>\r\nSpatial and conceptual development</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class="left-p">\r\n     <p>\r\nProblem-solving and analytical skills<p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="program-table">\r\n   <div class="left-p">\r\n      <p>\r\nSpatial and conceptual development</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class="left-p">\r\n     <p>\r\nProblem-solving and analytical skills<p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="program-table">\r\n   <div class="left-p">\r\n      <p>\r\nSpatial and conceptual development</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class="left-p">\r\n     <p>\r\nProblem-solving and analytical skills<p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="program-table">\r\n   <div class="left-p">\r\n      <p>\r\nSpatial and conceptual development</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class="left-p">\r\n     <p>\r\nProblem-solving and analytical skills<p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Find out why so many parents and students love Kidizens. Watch our testimonials or contact us for more information.</p>', 'Programs', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'programs', '', '', '2016-12-13 11:12:16', '2016-12-13 11:12:16', '', 0, 'http://anvinfosystem.com/project/kid/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
