(21, 1, '2016-11-18 16:44:17', '2016-11-18 16:44:17', '<p>Kidizens has multiple locations in the Bay area in California. Contact us to learn more or register online today for one of our programs.</p>\r\n<h5>Los Altos/ Palo Alto 4546 El Camino Real, Suite B9, Los Altos</h5>\r\n<p>Serving the Palo Alto, Los Altos, Mountain View and Menlo Park markets</p>\r\n<p>After successful years of operation in Palo Alto, we are excited to have found a permanent home. Our location is conveniently located at the border of Palo Alto, Los Altos and Mountain View. It is at the Village Court Center at 4546 El Camino Real, Suite B9, Los Altos, at the intersection of San Antonio Road and El Camino Real, with easy access from Loucks Avenue.</p>\r\n<iframe src="https://maps.google.com/maps?near=4546+El+Camino+Real,+Village+Court+Shopping+Center,+Los+Altos,+CA+94022&amp;geocode=CecNVyUX6BcPFUuwOgIdm6u4-ClzmQF5m7CPgDGRKsbVa4ROeA&amp;q=kidizens&amp;f=l&amp;hl=en&amp;sll=37.400659,-122.115183&amp;sspn=0.011302,0.021865&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=kidizens&amp;hnear=&amp;ll=37.400651,-122.115173&amp;spn=0.011302,0.021865&amp;t=h&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=A&amp;cid=3608808236893631233&amp;output=embed" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no" width="595" height="350" frameborder="0" class="location-map"></iframe>\r\n<p>Please email us at info@kidzzinc.com in order to schedule a visit.</p>\r\n<h5>Saratoga Location</h5>\r\n<p>12302 Saratoga Sunnyvale Road, Saratoga 95070\r\nServing Saratoga, Cupertino, Sunnyvale, Santa Clara and Los Gatos Markets</p>\r\n<p><b>We’re super excited to announce the opening of our new location in Saratoga. Our location is conveniently located on Saratoga Sunnyvale Road (Route 9) in Saratoga, half a mile from the Cupertino border and only a couple of miles from the Cupertino library.</b></p>\r\n<iframe class="location-map" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3174.2457412146987!2d-122.0318044!3d37.28930929999999!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x808fb5242d