(42, 1, '2016-11-18 16:57:33', '2016-11-18 16:57:33', '				<br/><br/>\r\n							<p>\r\n							We continue to be excited about Young Kidizens as a perfect beginning to our Kidizens program.  Our unique constructivist framework of city-building, role-playing and social learning enables groups of younger students to take on a guided discovery of real-life concepts.  While the overall concept and experiential learning philosophy of Kidizens penetrates all our programs, our curriculum for the “Young Kidizens,” is designed specifically for the target age group of 6-7 (and young 8’s), with the goal of simplifying many civic and economic concepts and bringing them to life with many play-based elements.\r\n							</p>\r\n							<p>\r\n							Please visit our Fall and Spring semester options to enroll in the program. Please send an email to info@kidzzinc.com if you have any questions.\r\n							</p>\r\n', 'Young Kidizens', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'young-kidizens', '', '', '2017-01-12 13:17:05', '2017-01-12 13:17:05', '', 11, 'http://anvinfosystem.com/project/kid/?page_id=42', 0, 'page', '', 0),
