(60, 1, '2016-11-18 17:01:56', '2016-11-18 17:01:56', '<p>Kidizens offers flexible pricing and scheduling options for parents whose students are interested in joining our unique LEGO-based social learning environment.\r\nBelow is a summary of our programs and pricing. Click on each individual program to learn more details.</p>\r\n\r\n<table class="table-fill">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th class="text-left">Fall 2016 Programs</th>\r\n<th class="text-left">Early-Bird Prices for Fall 2016 (14-Week Session)</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody class="table-hover">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="text-left">Kidizens</td>\r\n<td class="text-left">$588</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="text-left">Young Kidizens</td>\r\n<td class="text-left">$470</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="text-left">Kidizens Leadership Program</td>\r\n<td class="text-left">$610</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="text-left">Young Senators</td>\r\n<td class="text-left">$610</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="text-left">Robotizes</td>\r\n<td class="text-left">$350; 9 Weeks; Two 9-week sessions offered this Spring; Please email for exact details</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="text-left">Kinderzens</td>\r\n<td class="text-left">$430</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="text-left">Camps</td>\r\n<td class="text-left">Summer 1-Week Camp: $475 (Early-Bird Discount up to April 1st, $25)\r\nSummer 2-Week Camp: $820 ((Early-Bird Discount up to April 1st, $21)\r\n1-Day Workshop (9am to 3pm) – $95 – $105\r\n2-Day Workshop (9am to 3pm) – $180 – $210\r\n3-Day Workshop – $270 – $299\r\nHalf-Day Mini-Workshop – $45-$55</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="text-left">Drop-in Sessions</td>\r\n<td class="text-left">$ 18/hour/child (A group of 5 kids or more required)\r\nLos Altos: Every Friday 1pm – 5pm;\r\nSaratoga: Every Thursday 3:30pm – 5:30pm; Select Saturdays 10am – 12pm\r\nBelmont: Every Monday 2pm – 5pm and Every Friday 3pm – 5pm\r\npl email info@kidzzinc.com to confirm and for other days/times.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="text-left">Birthday Parties</td>\r\n<td class="text-left">$25/child; $250 minimum; Call for pricing for larger groups</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="text-left">LEGO Social Skills Workshop</td>\r\n<td class="text-left">Pl send us an email if you are interested</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Have questions? Contact us today and we’ll be happy to help you select the program that is right for your child.\r\n</p>', 'Pricing', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'pricing', '', '', '2016-12-15 09:18:08', '2016-12-15 09:18:08', '', 11, 'http://anvinfosystem.com/project/kid/?page_id=60', 0, 'page', '', 0),
