g, and the outdoors.</p>', 'Staff', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-26 13:42:05', '2016-11-26 13:42:05', '', 19, 'http://anvinfosystem.com/project/kid/2016/11/26/19-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
