(340, 1, '2016-12-06 09:41:04', '2016-12-06 09:41:04', '<h4 class="title">Kidizens Lego Summer Camps for the Bay Area</h4>\r\n                            <p><b>Would you like to build and be the Mayor of an entire city of LEGOs?\r\n							<br/>\r\nWould you like to leverage your love of LEGOs to learn about critical real-life lessons and strategies?\r\n</b></p>\r\n<p><b>Join us for one to two weeks of fun and responsibility at our very popular Kidizens Summer Camps at any one of our locations, in Los Altos, Belmont and Saratoga!</b></p>\r\n							<p>Another successful and creative round of Summer Camps has come to a close after the creation of over 150 thriving metropolises buzzing with the hustle and bustle of city life.</p>\r\n							<p>\r\n								Please check out of Fall and Winter Camps and our Fall Programs if you are interested in joining our journey as Kidizens.\r\n							</p>\r\n							<p>Registration for next years Summer Camp program opens November 21st 2016.</p>\r\n							<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vcd35Y-Y5_E" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>\r\n', 'LEGO Summer Camps', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-06 09:41:04', '2016-12-06 09:41:04', '', 36, 'http://anvinfosystem.com/project/kid/2016/12/06/36-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
