(356, 1, '2016-12-06 13:58:08', '2016-12-06 13:58:08', '<h4 class="title">LEGO Fall and Winter Camps</h4>\r\n							<br/><br/>\r\n							<h4 class="title">Kidizens Fall/Winter 2016-2017 LEGO Camps and Workshops</h4>\r\n                            <p><b>At our Fall/ Winter workshops the kids are age-appropriately partnered to build cities and solve civic/economic problems and take decisions to form a well functioning society. The kids face challenges and crises along the way and end the workshop evaluating city economy and overall citizen happiness, in addition to putting some laws and services in place — and of course, having lots of fun while doing so! Offered on staff development days, school holidays or in-service days. For list of additional workshops, please see the schedule below.</b></p>\r\n							<h5>1-Day Holiday Workshops</h5>\r\n<p>Our 1-day workshops feature unique, immersive themes – including city building, space exploration or an explorer, gold rush experience!\r\nOffered at all our locations: <b>Martin Luther King Day; Jan 16th;</b> 9am to 3:00pm; After-care available until 5pm at additional cost</p>\r\n					<h5>Thanksgiving 2-day Workshops: Nov 21st-22nd</h5>\r\n			<p>2-day workshops where the kids think, plan and build cities, while solving many problems along the way.<br/>\r\nOffered at all our locations: Nov 21st – 22nd from 9am to 3:00pm;<br/>\r\nAfter-care available until 5pm</p>\r\n<h5>Winter Camps: Dec 19th-21st and Dec 28th – 30th; 9am to 3:00pm</h5>\r\n<p>3-day winter workshops where the kids immerse themselves a bit deeper in the cities they build, solve civic/economic problems and take decisions to form a well functioning society.<br/>\r\nOffered at all our locations: Dec 19th-21st and Dec 28th-30th, from 9am to 3:00pm; After-care available until 5pm</p>\r\n<h6>Registration is now open for all of these workshops. In addition, check out our special drop-in sessions if you want to spend a part of the day with us or please contact us if you would like to schedule an extended, customized drop-in session with a group of kids. Many drop-in sessions available during the holidays.</h6>\r\n							<br/>\r\n							<p><b>Pl send us an email at info@kidzzinc.com, if you’re looking for a particular holiday camp and don’t see it listed here. Thanks!</b></p>', 'LEGO Fall and Winter Camps', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-06 13:58:08', '2016-12-06 13:58:08', '', 32, 'http://anvinfosystem.com/project/kid/2016/12/06/32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
