n<p><a href="https://www.activityhero.com/widgets/1441" class="register-button" target="_blank">Register</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h6><b>II. Two-week Options</b></h6>\r\n<div class="listing">\r\n<p>offered at the Kidizens Los Altos location, 4546 El Camino Real, Suite B9, only)</p>\r\n<p><b>June 12th  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;June 26th* &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;July 10th &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;July 24th  \r\n</b></p>\r\n<p><b>For Los Altos 2-Week Summer Camps, Register Here:  </b></p>\r\n<p><a href="https://www.activityhero.com/widgets/1494" class="register-button" target="_blank">Register</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="listing">\r\n<h5>A few things to note: </h5>\r\n<p>*Aftercare provided until 5pm at additional cost</p>\r\n<p>*Daily walks to a nearby park for lunch and city-related, civic games</p>\r\n<p>*Healthy Snacks provided morning and afternoon</p>\r\n<p>*Free lunch provided on Wednesdays; Please bring easy-to-carry, nut-free lunch all other days.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Please email <b>info@kidzzinc.com</b> if you have any questions pertaining to any of the summer camps.</p>\r\n<p>Our camps offer a great opportunity for high-schoolers and middle-schoolers.&nbsp;Please click here for more information relating to&nbsp;Kidizens Volunteer and Intern opportunities&nbsp;this summer</p>\r\n', 'summer-2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '656-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-15 13:13:38', '2017-02-15 13:13:38', '', 656, 'http://anvinfosystem.com/project/kid/2017/02/15/656-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
